      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Start with the business problem.\n- Pharma Company is relying more heavily on CMOs.\n- That means more invoices, more contract terms, and more chances for payment mistakes.\n- Before we open the app, frame why invoice review got harder to trust.",
      "demo_actions": "Open on a simple title or framing slide. Introduce the rise in CMO activity and invoice complexity before showing product screens.",
