        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "- The issue is not one bad invoice.\n- It is the growing mix of rates, milestones, batch releases, approvals, and exceptions.\n- Payment teams have to piece together the full story before money goes out.\n- That takes time, and it leaves room for leakage.",
      "demo_actions": "Use a framing visual or simple supporting graphic that lists the main sources of complexity: contract terms, receipts, batch records, QA release, approvals, and invoice lines.",
      "screenshot": null
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
