        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- When that review stays manual, the business feels it fast.\n- Decisions slow down.\n- Confidence drops.\n- And disputed or overbilled amounts get harder to catch early.",
      "demo_actions": "Advance to a concise business-impact view with three outcomes: slower decisions, lower confidence, and payment leakage.",
